⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Mute Master
node M1 · M1 · ⟦The Mute Master:M1:9ae47e⟧

WHO   — The Mute Master — Master of the Silent Assassins
WHAT  — A mentor of The Assassin's Blade — the warlord-scholar of a desert keep whose fighters answer to gesture and gaze alone, who measures a killer not by her reputation but by what she is willing to learn.
WHERE — M1 · Maas  Framework inputs: Throne of Glass — The Assassin's Blade  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because true mastery is quiet and earned, not loud and bought; because a fighter who cannot still herself cannot truly be deadly; because a blessing freely given is a thing of weight, owed to no one but the one who proves worthy of it.
HOW   — By patience, presence, and a discipline beyond speech; by the training of the Silent Assassins; by the keen judgment that reads a guest's heart — and the rare token of approval he grants only when it is deserved.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I do not need words to be heard — and I do not give my blessing to the unworthy.

